item.title: CVE-2023-38422|2024-10-03T13:40:49.576Z -- walchem -- intuition%209
item.description: Walchem Intuition 9 firmware versions prior to v4.21 are missing authentication for some of the API routes of the management web server. This could allow an attacker to download and export sensitive data.
